TASK_UPDATED=1774980771
TASK_LOG_1774982070=COMPLETE: Committed dc22813. Viewport scrolling added to TUI task detail view.
TASK_RESULT=Replaced manual rightScroll with Bubble Tea viewport. All keys work (arrows, j/k, pgup/pgdn, home/end, mouse wheel). go build and go test pass.
TASK_FILES=tui/internal/model/tasks.go,tui/internal/taskcard/taskcard.go
TASK_DECISION_LOG=1774982193:Task complete. Viewport scrolling implemented in tasks.go. Committed dc22813.
